  {"column": "___subject", "path": "$.subject"},
  {"column": "station_number", "path": "$.station_number"},
  {"column": "formula", "path": "$.formula"},
  {"column": "value", "path": "$.value"},
  {"column": "timestamp_measured", "path": "$.timestamp_measured"},
]
```

